## PRD — Predefined Service: HubSpot Marketing Hub Onboarding (Full, Updated)

**Priority:** 🔴 High  
**Service type:** Predefined consulting service  
**Applies to:** Superwork customer portal  
**Depends on:** Projects, SOPs, Tasks, Milestones, Permissions, Progress Tracking

---

## 1. Purpose

Define a **single, standardized predefined service** called:

> **HubSpot Marketing Hub Onboarding**

This service is intentionally scoped to **Marketing Hub only**.  
Other hubs (Sales, Service, Content, Data, Commerce) are separate services with their own PRDs.

This service:
- Has a fixed, standardized project description
- Uses one internal SOP (provider/admin only)
- Generates a customer-visible task list and milestones
- Tracks progress purely based on completed tasks
- Allows providers/admins to add custom tasks when required

